From 288dd520dfe2e9cc237b8c0abad03b803f9ae4fd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: skinny-l <azizdj2002@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 11:48:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add dispatch table parsing, merge into ticket jobs

- fiars/parser_table.py: parse pasted dispatch/assignment table
  (Date, Ticket No#, Case ID#, Server SN, Rack Info, Faulty Part,
  OLD PN, NEW PN, Maker, Model, Engineer), match rows to parsed
  ticket jobs by Server SN -> category -> order of appearance.
- Auto-fills ticket_number and old/new PN instead of manual entry.
- Case ID# parsed but unused. Engineer parsed but not merged.
  Maker/Model kept as server_model_code metadata, not part fields.
- report.py: old.pn/new.pn now read from the merge, default blank
  when no dispatch table is supplied (backward compatible).
- server.py: /api/parse accepts optional dispatch_table field.
- templates/index.html: optional second textarea for the paste.
- tests/test_parser_table.py: 9 tests covering parse, merge,
  category disambiguation, no-match safety, and the report
  end-to-end.
